com.mobilecoin.lib

Class Receipt

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mobilecoin.lib.Receipt

  • public class Receipt
extends Object
    This receipt is created by MobileCoinClient.prepareTransaction(PublicAddress, BigInteger, BigInteger) Then shared with the recipient, so they can check the transaction status. Only the recipient can use this receipt since it requires a recipient's key for decoding.
